     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"There are defined grounds on which we will accept a representation against a Penalty Charge Notice (PCN).\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "In all cases, please ensure that you make a representation within 28 days of the date of service of the PCN.",
     "Find out more about challenging a PCN.",
     "Your PCN will also clearly state for which contravention it has been issued and will set out the grounds on which you can make a representation.",
     "You may make representations on any of the eight grounds below and raise any other mitigating circumstances.",
